# QA Project Structure

When generating QA artifacts, save outputs to these project-relative directories.
Create the directory on first use if it does not exist.

| Skill | Output Directory | File Pattern |
|-------|-----------------|--------------|
| qa-requirements-generator | `docs/requirements/` | `REQ-{feature}.md` |
| qa-spec-writer | `docs/specs/` | `SPEC-{feature}.md` |
| qa-plan-creator | `docs/plans/` | `{plan-type}-plan.md` |
| qa-test-strategy | `docs/plans/` | `test-strategy.md` |
| qa-discovery-interview | `docs/briefs/` | `brief-{project}.md` |
| qa-bug-ticket-creator | `docs/bug-tickets/` | `BUG-{id}.md` |
| qa-diagram-generator | `docs/diagrams/` | `{type}-{name}.md` |
| qa-nfr-analyst | `docs/nfr/` | `NFR-{feature}.md` |
| qa-api-contract-curator | `docs/api-contracts/` | `{service}.openapi.yaml` |
| qa-test-doc-compiler | `docs/compiled/` | `{doc-type}-{date}.md` |
| qa-testcase-from-docs | `test-cases/from-docs/` | `TC-{feature}.md` |
| qa-testcase-from-ui | `test-cases/from-ui/` | `TC-UI-{page}.md` |
| qa-manual-test-designer | `test-cases/manual/` | `MTC-{feature}.md` |
| qa-jest-writer | `tests/unit/` | `{name}.test.ts` |
| qa-vitest-writer | `tests/unit/` | `{name}.test.ts` |
| qa-pytest-writer | `tests/unit/` | `test_{name}.py` |
| qa-junit5-writer | `tests/unit/` | `{Name}Test.java` |
