| qa-selenium-py-writer | `tests/e2e/` | `test_{name}.py` |
| qa-selenium-java-writer | `tests/e2e/` | `{Name}Test.java` |
| qa-webdriverio-writer | `tests/e2e/` | `{name}.e2e.ts` |
| qa-codeceptjs-writer | `tests/e2e/` | `{name}.test.ts` |
| qa-robot-framework-writer | `tests/e2e/` | `{name}.robot` |
